title: ERA MSS TX transmitters
agents: snmp
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Walks the tx sub-table under OID .1.3.6.1.4.1.11588.1.5.103.1 and creates one
 service per transmitter site. Reports the status cells txStatus, txLan1,
 txLan2, txOutPower, txVSWR, txOutPul, txNtpComm, txDutyCycle, txInputData,
 txOverheating, txPower plus informational addresses (txModesAddr, txLan1Addr,
 txLan2Addr).

item:
 Transmitter site name (txSiteName).

inventory:
 One service per TX site with a non-empty site name.
